I"u<h1 id="main-buttons">Main Buttons</h1>

<p>The main buttons in our application are used to login/logout and for the uploadform. Because Ruby on Rails mainly uses the button-tag to send a form, we used a link-tags most of the time and gave them the button styles.
The first one is the link-tag, the second is the button-tag.</p>

