<p>A button can be disabled, pointer events will not occur.</p>

<h1 id="ghost-buttons">Ghost Buttons</h1>

<p>The ghost buttons are used in smaller elements of our application. For example to show idividual challenges or posts, or as a link to another page of the project. Like we did with the main buttons, we also mainly used link-tags and styled them accordingly. The only time we used a button-tag was on our filter-form.</p>

